<HEADER>
A2390 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOLD-CAMPUS-CREDIT-BO     09-18 0050
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HOLD-CAMPUS-CREDIT-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   The undatelined story BC-CAMPUS-CREDIT-BOS, by Patricia Wen, has
been HELD. Please guard against premature release. We will advise
you when the story may be used.
</P>
<P>
   Repeat: BC-CAMPUS-CREDIT-BOS as been HELD.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
