<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-18 13:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2722 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MUSIC-NUGGET-BOS &LR;      09-18 1001
