<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MOTOROLA-INTERNET (Undated) -- While Motorola Inc.'s core
wireless and seminconductor businesses are struggling, its Internet
and networking division is developing leading-edge technologies
that could help its turnaround efforts. By Joann Muller.
</P>
<P>
