   SUNDAY FINANCIAL
</P>
<P>
   Here is a preliminary look at the graphics scheduled for the
Sunday financial section of The Times. These graphics will be
transmitted Friday evening. The descriptions and sizes are
tentative. Please check tomorrow's late budget for stories and
specific graphics.
</P>
<P>
   IN-MY/Briefcase.pdf -- 4 x 3 -- Weekly financial feature.
</P>
<P>
   An annotated look at Jeffrey Sachs' briefcase. Pdf file.
</P>
<P>
   STOCKS/Highlight 9-20 -- 38p6 x 8 1/4 -- Weekly financial chart.
</P>
<P>
   Highlighting of an assortment of stocks.
