 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE SATURDAY SPORTS BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These sports stories for release on Saturday, September 19,
1998, are moving today to clients of the New York Times News
Service.
</P>
<P>
   All stories have moved except those with an ETA.
</P>
<P>
   If you have questions or need a resend, please call CoxNet, the
