<P>
   BOX-EVANDER _ ATLANTA _ Evander Holyfield tonight stages the
third, and likely last, pro bout of his glorious career at the
Georgia Dome. He hopes to parlay a win over Vaugh Bean into a title
unification bout with Lennox Lewis. (Schultz, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
