IMMIGRANT ADVOCATES SAY MINORS BEING HELD IN ADULT DETENTION CAMP 
 
By JAMES PINKERTON 
c.1998 Houston Chronicle 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   HARLINGEN _ Dentists are not authorities on immigration law, but
they often determine who gets locked up in a detention camp.
</P>
<P>
   Cu7O~9r9Q1eX
