<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-18 18:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3329 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT/FEATURE-BUDGET-B     09-18 0804
</HEADER>
