stereotypes. Is Hillary a suffering wife, a conniving wife or a
business partner? We cannot know, but the popular press squeezes
her _ and everyone else involved _ into the tight shackles of
melodrama. So little imagination. It is as if the whole plot were
dreamed up in a trailer park. By RICHARD NILSEN. Story will move in
