<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-18 19:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3417 &Cx1f; tth-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BUDGET-SPOT-SPI &LR;      09-18 0143
</HEADER>
<BODY>
