 &UR; By BILL CARTER &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; FROM: The New York Times Magazine &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; For release: Sept. 20 or thereafter &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   When NBC agreed to pay $13 million per episode for ``E.R.'', the
network didn't just buy a guaranteed hit _ it almost bought the
farm.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Bill Carter covers television for The New York Times. (slugged:
BC-E.R.-CENTERPIECE-$adv20-NYTSF, priority code s, category code
c) &LR;
